!theme retro-coast from ../themes/retro-coast



person Person <<Person>> [
  == Person
  Person
]

actor Actor <<fg>> <<Person>> [
  == Actor
  Actor
]

package "System Boundary" <<dashed>> <<System>> {
    component SoftwareSystem <<System>> [
    == Software System
    Software System
  ]


  component SoftwareSystem2 <<Software System>> [
    == Software System
    Software System
  ]

  component Container <<Container>> [
    == Container
    Container
  ]

  component Component <<Component>> [
    == Component
    Component
  ]
}

person ExternalPerson <<External Person>> [
  == External Person
  External Person
]

actor ExternalActor <<fg>> <<External Person>> [
  == External Actor
  External Actor
]

package "External System Boundary" <<dashed>> <<External System>> {
    component ExternalSoftwareSystem <<External System>> [
    == External Software System
    External Software System
  ]


  component ExternalSoftwareSystem2 <<External Software System>> [
    == External Software System
    External Software System
  ]

  component ExternalContainer <<External Container>> [
    == External Container
    External Container
  ]

  component ExternalComponent <<External Component>> [
    == External Component
    External Component
  ]
}


SoftwareSystem -r-> Container : says hello to
Container .r.> Component: says hello to\n[async, HTTPS]

[System Boundary] -d[hidden]-> [External System Boundary]

ExternalSoftwareSystem -r-> ExternalContainer : says hello to
ExternalContainer .r.> ExternalComponent: "says hello to\n[async, HTTPS]"


@enduml